instructions: put the charger on the bottom of the table
put the dinner fork on the left side of the charger with its prong pointed upward
put the dinner knife on the right side of the charger with its blade pointed left
put the salad fork on the left side of the dinner fork with its tines pointed upward
put the salad knife on the right side of the dinner knife
put the soup sponn on the right side of the salad knife
put the dessert spoon above the charger with the bowl on the left
put the dessert between the charger and the dessert spoon with tines pointed right
put the bread plate upwards and to the left of the dinner plate
put the butter knife on the bread plate pointed up and to the left
put the water glass above the salad knife
put the napkin on the plate
